="d-sm-flex flex-sm-column flex-lg-row pb-lg-4"><div class="col-lg-4 text-center border-line-bottom-small border-line-right pt-4"><p class="fs-400 mb-0 fw-bold">WE SEND</p><p class="fs-700 header-font fw-bold my-4">180K+</p><p>DMARC REPORTS<br>PER WEEK</p></div><div class="col-lg-4 text-center border-line-bottom-small border-line-right pt-4"><p class="fs-400 mb-0 fw-bold">WE CHECK</p><p class="fs-700 header-font fw-bold my-4">15K+</p><p>PHISHING URLS<br>PER WEEK</p></div><div class="col-lg-4 text-center pt-4 pb-3 pb-md-0"><p class="fs-400 mb-0 fw-bold">WE MONITOR</p><p class="fs-700 header-font fw-bold my-4">14K+</p><p>DOMAINS<br>PER WEEK</p></div></div></div></div></section> <section class="py-5 position-relative domains-map-container"><div class="container my-3 position-relative z-index-11"><h2 class="domains-map-title text-center text-headline mb-5 pb-lg-5">175,000+ domains from 130 countries</h2><picture><source srcset="/img/domains-map-mobile.webp" media="(max-width: 768px)"><img src="/img/domains-map.webp" width="1446" height="707" loading="lazy" class="m-auto fade-in" alt="Domains map"></picture><div class="domains-map-desc mt-4"><p class="text-primary-blue-dark-60 fw-bold header-font fs-500 mb-4 text-nowrap text-uppercase">Global presence</p><span class="eas-tag eas-tag--blue-dark mx-auto ms-lg-0">4 Offices</span><p class="text-primary-blue-dark-70 mt-3">US, UK, Netherlands & Armenia</p></div></div><div class="shadow-gradient"></div></section> <section class="pb-5"><div class="container great-companies-container position-relative z-index-11"><h3 class="text-headline text-center mb-2">Great companies meet and beat compliance with EasyDMARC</h3><p class="text-primary-blue-dark-50 text-center">Discover shared thoughts and learn more about businesses growing safely with EasyDMARC.</p><div class="position-relative z-index-11 mt-5">  <div class="d-flex flex-column flex-lg-row justify-content-between"><div class="position-relative card-white-bg"><div class="great-c